Home				CANT JOIN DOMAIN or USE GPE
Pro/Enterprise/Education	CAN JOIN DOMAIN or USE GPE

gpedit.msc	(Local) Group Policy Editor		Global
secpol.msc	Local Security Policy (Editor)		Local - brother of GPE

